#LightCoral\n  participant "BloodInventoryDatabase" as DB\n  participant "InventoryManagementAPI" as API\nend box\n\n== 
Reserve Blood Unit ==\n\nUI -> Service : reserveBloodUnit(requestId: String, bloodType: String, components: 
Set<ComponentType>) : Reservation\nnote right: Requires Write permission (BloodBankManager only)\n\nService -> API : 
checkAvailability(bloodType: String, components: Set<ComponentType>) : Boolean\nnote right: [TLS encrypted] 
[authenticated]\n\nalt Insufficient inventory\n  API --> Service : return false\n  Service --> UI : return error 
"Insufficient inventory"\n  UI -> UI : display error to BloodBankManager\nelse Inventory available\n  API --> Service : 
return true\n  \n  Service -> DB : beginTransaction()\n  note right: Atomic check-and-reserve\n  \n  Service -> API : 
reserveUnit(bloodType: String, components: Set<ComponentType>) : BloodUnit\n  note right: [TLS encrypted] [authenticated]\n  
\n  alt Race condition - unit already reserved\n    API --> Service : return error "Unit already reserved"\n    Service -> DB
: rollback()\n    Service --> UI : return error "Concurrent reservation detected"\n  else Unit successfully reserved\n    API
--> Service : return bloodUnit: BloodUnit\n    \n    Service -> BU : setStatus(status: BloodUnitStatus.RESERVED)\n    note 
right: State transition: Available -> Reserved\n    Service -> BU : setReservedFor(requestId: String)\n    \n    Service -> 
Clock : getCurrentTimestamp() : Timestamp\n    Clock --> Service : timestamp\n    \n    alt timeoutDuration == 0\n      
Service -> Res : create(request: TransfusionRequest, unit: BloodUnit, reservedAt: Timestamp, timeoutDuration: 0)\n      
Service -> BU : setStatus(status: BloodUnitStatus.AVAILABLE)\n      note right: Immediate release\n      Service -> BU : 
clearReservedFor()\n      Service -> DB : deleteReservation(reservationId: String)\n      Service -> DB : commit()\n      
Service --> UI : return error "Zero timeout - immediate release"\n    else timeoutDuration > 0\n      Service -> Res : 
create(request: TransfusionRequest, unit: BloodUnit, reservedAt: Timestamp, timeoutDuration: Duration)\n      Service -> DB :
saveReservation(reservation: Reservation)\n      Service -> DB : updateBloodUnitStatus(unitId: String, status: 
BloodUnitStatus.RESERVED)\n      Service -> DB : commit()\n      \n      Service -> Scheduler : 
scheduleTimeout(reservationId: String, timeoutDuration: Duration)\n      note right: Schedule auto-release handler\n      \n 
Service --> UI : return reservation: Reservation\n      UI -> UI : display success to BloodBankManager\n    end\n  
end\nend\n\n== Auto Release on Timeout ==\n\nScheduler -> Service : handleTimeout(reservationId: String)\nnote right: 
Triggered by SystemClock\n\nService -> DB : beginTransaction()\nService -> DB : loadReservation(reservationId: String) : 
Reservation\nDB --> Service : reservation: Reservation\n\nalt Reservation not found\n  Service -> DB : rollback()\n  Service 
--> Scheduler : return error "Reservation already released"\nelse Reservation found\n  Service -> DB : loadBloodUnit(unitId: 
String) : BloodUnit\n  DB --> Service : bloodUnit: BloodUnit\n  \n  alt BloodUnit status != RESERVED\n    Service -> DB : 
rollback()\n    Service --> Scheduler : return error "Unit already released"\n  else BloodUnit status == RESERVED\n    
Service -> BU : setStatus(status: BloodUnitStatus.AVAILABLE)\n    note right: State transition: Reserved -> Available\n    
Service -> BU : clearReservedFor()\n    \n    Service -> DB : updateBloodUnitStatus(unitId: String, status: 
BloodUnitStatus.AVAILABLE)\n    Service -> DB : deleteReservation(reservationId: String)\n    Service -> DB : commit()\n    
\n    Service --> Scheduler : return success\n  end\nend\n\n== Release on Cancellation ==\n\nUI -> Service : 
cancelRequest(requestId: String)\nnote right: Requires Write permission (BloodBankManager only)\n\nService -> DB : 
beginTransaction()\nnote right: Atomic release of all associated units\n\nService -> DB : loadTransfusionRequest(requestId: 
String) : TransfusionRequest\nDB --> Service : request: TransfusionRequest\n\nalt Request not found\n  Service -> DB : 
rollback()\n  Service --> UI : return error "Request not found"\nelse Request status != PENDING\n  Service -> DB : 
rollback()\n  Service --> UI : return error "Request already cancelled or fulfilled"\nelse Request status == PENDING\n  
Service -> DB : loadReservationsByRequest(requestId: String) : List<Reservation>\n  DB --> Service : reservations: 
List<Reservation>\n  \n  alt No reservations found\n    Service -> TR : setStatus(status: 
TransfusionRequestStatus.CANCELLED)\n    Service -> DB : updateRequestStatus(requestId: String, status: 
TransfusionRequestStatus.CANCELLED)\n    Service -> DB : commit()\n    Service --> UI : return success\n  else Reservations 
found\n    loop for each reservation in reservations\n      Service -> DB : loadBloodUnit(unitId: String) : BloodUnit\n      
DB --> Service : bloodUnit: BloodUnit\n      \n      Service -> BU : setStatus(status: BloodUnitStatus.AVAILABLE)\n      note
right: State transition: Reserved -> Available\n      Service -> BU : clearReservedFor()\n      \n      Service -> DB : 
updateBloodUnitStatus(unitId: String, status: BloodUnitStatus.AVAILABLE)\n      Service -> DB : 
deleteReservation(reservationId: String)\n      \n      Service -> Scheduler : cancelTimeout(reservationId: String)\n      
note right: Prevent double release\n    end\n    \n    Service -> TR : setStatus(status: 
TransfusionRequestStatus.CANCELLED)\n    note right: State transition: Pending -> Cancelled\n    Service -> DB : 
updateRequestStatus(requestId: String, status: TransfusionRequestStatus.CANCELLED)\n    Service -> DB : commit()\n    \n    
Service --> UI : return success\n    UI -> UI : display cancellation confirmation\n  end\nend\n\n@enduml', 
